Police suspect 37-year-old Philani Mdluli was kidnapped, drugged and later murdered by a male friend. JOHANNESBURG - The body of a missing police officer has been found near Sabie in Nelspruit.Police suspect 37-year-old Philani Mdluli was kidnapped, drugged and later murdered by a male friend. The police's Leonard Hlathi says the suspect will appear at the Nelspruit Magistrate Court soon. The provincial commissioner has indicated that police killings are high on the priority [list] in terms of policing in the country and we will sure leave no stone unturned. 